snippet.title: Switch & Lever
snippet.description:
A mixture of machine shop, wood working, programming and prototype building videos, all in one dandy package.
Companion to the site http://www.switchandlever.com

Contact me for business inquiries, collaborations or sponsorship deals. 

Kindly refrain from contacting me about joining a YouTube network. My channel is network free, and will continue to be so!
